    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one! It's always been garaged, meticulously cared for, and still has that fresh, new-car feel inside and out. It runs like an absolute dream and is in truly pristine condition. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
