    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional specimen that presents in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a factory-fresh appearance that must be seen to be appreciated. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep gloss with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the trim remains supple and unfaded. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and the dashboard is free of any imperfections. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the smallest interior light, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a complete, chronological service history performed exclusively by authorized specialists. It delivers a driving experience that is tight, quiet, and indistinguishable from new. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is an unrivaled opportunity.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
